title: For Sale:  Israeli Made Uzi 9mm price reduced
postcontent: This is a very nice Uzi it has upgraded Iseali made parts, and a bag of extra parts like top cover, grips, stock etc. Will come with 2 uzi mags i belive they are 22 round mags. Uzi mags are cheap and can be bought on line in bulk. it comes with a thick barrel shroud balances out the weapon nicely and also makes it look cooler. it unscrews if you dont like it. This one has the Star of David scratched but you can see it was there. that means this was an original Israeli made Uzi. to bring it into the states the import company had to debadge the star of david on it. the Star is still there, they just ground out the center circle of it.  Some sort of old importation BS back in the day.  Then the outer shell parts were us or suprlus made, they have been replaced with Israeli parts now, and also the originals come with it. The stock folds and locks tight. it deploys with a very cool slap of the hand. The sights on this gun are amazing. I hate iron sights and always go with a scope or red dot.  on this one the irons provide a very clear and immediate sight picture, as soon as i bring it up I am looking down the sights and the front post is on target, its eas to see the target and move around as well. Uzi is like the AK of pistol caliber rifles. it is made solid, i mean really solid a huge hunk of metal, and that makes it reliable and stable. it reduces the recoil a ton, and makes for a very soft shooting accurate carbine. the action is straight blow back on a heavy brick of a bolt on a large spring system, its qucik efficient, and takes up recoil.  They used Uzis to protect the president for decades for many of these reasons. The downside is only that its a ittle heavy compared to other weapons that shoot 9mm these days.  but again if you want the nostalgia, the reliability, accuracy, and stright fun factor you wont feel the weight that much you will have adreneline helping you as you operate one of the worlds classic iconic sub machine guns- ( in semi auto)this one has been in my safe and planned to keep it forever but im kinda itching to buy a car so i need to sell some guns...will regret it later im sure. text me at REDACTED  cash only, no paypal,
